<h3 id="what-youll-need">What youâ€™ll need</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Android Phone (Mine is a Oneplus 2 running Android 6.0.1)</li>
  <li>USB Microphone (I own a <a href="https://www.amazon.in/Blue-Microphones-Snowball-MW-Microphone-Textured/dp/B000EOPQ7E">Blue Snowball USB Microphone</a>)</li>
